Class CalibratableComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.product.definition.Component
        • org.drip.product.definition.CalibratableComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentMarketParamRef
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreditComponent, RatesComponent

    public abstract class CalibratableComponent
extends Component
    This abstract class providing implementation of Component interface. Provides stub for getting the component’s primary code, and optionally provides multiple secondary codes.
